{"tid":1604659,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶) 烏大龜節錄","createTime":"2019-09-30T04:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T08:24:09.000Z","uid":219183,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d145fc8670fd6451ddcf6e8742dc987a72a8778","tid":1604659,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"烏大龜是站着計數而穿保安衫的唯一的人。他身材不高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；青白臉色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，皺紋間時常夾些傷痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；一部亂蓬蓬的花白的鬍子。穿的雖然是保安衫，可是又髒又破，似乎十多年沒有補，也沒有洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他對人說話，總是滿口MK behaviour，教人半懂不懂的。因爲他係龜，別人便從不文集上的「死毒撚OTAKU」這半懂不懂的話裏，替他取下一個綽號，叫作烏大龜。烏大龜一上線，所有連登的人便都看著他笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有的叫道，「烏大龜，你怎麼又回來校園台了！」他不回答，對admin說，「溫兩碗酒，要一本教科書。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />便排出九題數。他們又故意的高聲嚷道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，「你一定又被抄登巴打趕出來了！」烏大龜睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你被眾巴打恥笑，吊著打。」烏大龜便漲紅了臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，額上的青筋條條綻出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，爭辯道，「退出不能算趕&hellip;&hellip;退出！&hellip;&hellip;IQ135的ENTJ，還會被趕麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「Entering university is MK behaviour」，什麼「中化考得好都是狗公」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n聽人家背地裏談論，烏大龜原來也讀過書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但終於沒有學位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又不會擦鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；於是愈過愈窮，弄到要做保安了。幸而算得一手好數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，便替人家計計數，換一杯精飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。可惜他又有一樣壞脾氣，便是好吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬾含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。坐不到幾天，便連人和題目紙計算器，一齊失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如是幾次，叫他計數的人也沒有了。烏大龜沒有法，便免不了偶然做些MK behaviour<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但他在校園台裏，品行卻比別人都好，就是從不拖欠；<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然間或沒有題目，暫時記在粉板上，但不出一日，定然還清，從粉板上拭去了烏大龜的名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n烏大龜計過半條數，漲紅的臉色漸漸復了原<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，旁人便又問道，「烏大龜，你當眞認識數學麼？」烏大龜看着問他的人，顯出不屑置辯的神氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他們便接着說道，「你怎的連半個學位也撈不到呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />烏大龜立刻顯出頹唐不安模樣，臉上籠上了一層灰色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嘴裏說些話；這回可是全是MK behaviours 之類，一些不懂了。在這時候，衆人也都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n在這些時候，我可以附和着笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，admin是決不責備的。而且admin見了烏大龜，也每每這樣問他，引人發笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。烏大龜自己知道不能和他們談天，便只好向廢青說話。有一回對我說道，「你讀過書麼？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我略略點一點頭。他說，「讀過書，&hellip;&hellip;我便考你一考。這道中四數學題，怎樣算的？」我想，保安一樣的人，也配考我麼？便回過臉去，不再理會。烏大龜等了許久，很懇切的說道，「不能算罷？&hellip;&hellip;我教給你，記着！這些算術應該記着。將來做保安的時候，消磨時間要用。」我暗想我和保安的等級還很遠呢，而且我們保安也從不計數消磨時間；又好笑，又不耐煩，嬾嬾的答他道<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，「誰要你教，不是歐拉公式麼？」烏大龜顯出極高興的樣子，將兩個指頭的長指甲敲着櫃臺，點頭說，「對呀對呀！&hellip;&hellip;這道M2 數學題的解法，你知道麼？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愈不耐煩了，努着嘴走遠。烏大龜剛用指甲蘸了酒，想在櫃上計數，見我毫不熱心，便又歎一口氣，顯出極惋惜的樣子。<br />\n<br />\n有幾回，連登巴打聽得笑聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，也<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 趕熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，圍住了烏大龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。他便給他們數學題計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一人一題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。巴打計完數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仍然不散，眼睛都望着瑩幕。烏大龜着了慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，伸開五指將瑩幕罩住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，彎腰下去說道，「不多了，我已經不多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」直起身又看一看題，自己搖頭說，「不多不多！多乎哉？不多也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」於是這一羣巴打都在笑聲裏走散了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n烏大龜是這樣的使人快活，可是沒有他，別人也便這麼過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n有一天，admin正在慢慢的派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，取下粉板，忽然說，「烏大龜長久沒有來了。還欠十九條數呢！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我纔也覺得他的確長久沒有來了。一個吹水的人說道，「他怎麼會來？&hellip;&hellip;他打折了腿了。」admin說，「哦！」「他總仍舊去偷。這一回，是自己發昏，竟串到CUHKBanters家裏去了。他家的學位，偷得的麼？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「後來怎麼樣？」「怎麼樣？先寫服辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，後來是打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，打了大半夜，再打折了腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」「後來呢？」「後來打折了腿了。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「打折了怎樣呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「怎樣？&hellip;&hellip;誰曉得？許是死了。」admin也不再問，仍然慢慢的派他的膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n自此以後，又長久沒有看見烏大龜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我到現在終於沒有見&mdash;&mdash;大約烏大龜的確死了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56133262069461da5e792cb1a84d29c41605013d","tid":1604659,"uid":203657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"唔錯"},{"pid":"42adf3aae41f1afc323dea2051e4a8890c6c0834","tid":1604659,"uid":161462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"啲公仔好夾好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ff60baaf82f63ed69af3a509fcbd0fd2f90316","tid":1604659,"uid":175032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"挑<br />\n你自己咪又係校台老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6127138813d44d58147e5db5ff99b363c5f7a05b","tid":1604659,"uid":160884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"82ff60baaf82f63ed69af3a509fcbd0fd2f90316","tid":1604659,"uid":175032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"挑<br />\n你自己咪又係校台老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9ad076cbd834e2ad1280606eebd6d8950423e3","tid":1604659,"uid":29120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b07a7b9406db2fce5977d6bf0628738d7586c79e","tid":1604659,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"2c744f0233600e4c4d988d705ae43697bea9db1c","tid":1604659,"uid":29120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5af038bc5864e54d90e7af4acd4d171ae9d6fee5","tid":1604659,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:25:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db04a3de9fe52cf1c3955709400cd59dd86795ba","tid":1604659,"uid":377